{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/pages/jupyter-notebook-install","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ij.Log"}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>jupyter notebook 을 더 편하게 사용하기 위한 옵션 설정 등에 관한 포스트 입니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-install-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-install-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"1 install 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Install (설치)</h2>\n<h4 id=\"anaconda\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#anaconda\" aria-label=\"anaconda permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Anaconda</h4>\n<p>많은 사용자들이 anaconda를 통해 python 개발환경을 구성한다. anaconda를 설치하면 jupyter notebook은 자동으로 설치가 된다.\n아나콘다는 과학계산을 위한 Python / R 프로그래밍 언어 패키지 배포판이며, 아래 링크를 통해 다운로드가 가능하다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.anaconda.com/distribution/\">Anaconda Installer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.anaconda.com/anaconda/install/windows/\">Windows</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.anaconda.com/anaconda/install/mac-os/\">macOS</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"pip\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#pip\" aria-label=\"pip permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>pip</h4>\n<p>python을 이미 사용중이면 pip을 통해 설치할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">pip <span class=\"token function\">install</span> jupyter notebook</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"2-setting-config\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-setting-config\" aria-label=\"2 setting config permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Setting (config)</h2>\n<p>아래 명령어를 실행하여 jupyter notebook 설정을 위한 파일을 생성할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">jupyter notebook --generate-config\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># C:\\Users\\username\\.jupyter\\jupyter_notebook_config.py 파일 생성</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>jupyter_notebook_config.py 내부 파일은 주석 처리 상태로 효과가 없다.</li>\n<li>주석 해제와 값 설정을 통해 원하는 옵션을 지정 가능하다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"시작-디렉토리-설정-옵션\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91-%EB%94%94%EB%A0%89%ED%86%A0%EB%A6%AC-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95-%EC%98%B5%EC%85%98\" aria-label=\"시작 디렉토리 설정 옵션 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>시작 디렉토리 설정 옵션</h4>\n<p>원하는 작업 디렉토리에서 시작할 수 있도록 설정할 수 있는 옵션</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-python line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-python\"> <span class=\"token comment\">## The directory to use for notebooks and kernels.</span>\n c<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>NotebookApp<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>notebook_dir <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'C:\\\\Users\\\\USERNAME\\\\Documents\\\\workspace'</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>jupyter notebook 의 기본 시작 디렉토리는 C:/Users/USERNAME 이다.</li>\n<li>다른 작업 디렉토리가 존재한다면 위의 변수를 수정하여 작업디렉토리에서 jupyter notebook 이 실행되도록 변경할 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"3-extensions-확장-프로그램\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-extensions-%ED%99%95%EC%9E%A5-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%A8\" aria-label=\"3 extensions 확장 프로그램 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Extensions (확장 프로그램)</h2>\n<h3 id=\"확장-프로그램-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%99%95%EC%9E%A5-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%A8-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"확장 프로그램 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>확장 프로그램 설치</h3>\n<p>아래 명령어를 실행하여 conda 또는 pip 을 통해 확장프로그램 설치가 가능하다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token comment\"># install with anaconda </span>\nconda <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -c conda-forge jupyter_contrib_nbextensions \n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># install with pip</span>\npip <span class=\"token function\">install</span> jupyter_contrib_nbextensions</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>설치가 끝났다면 아래 명령어를 실행하여 활성화를 해주어야 한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">jupyter contrib nbextension <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --user</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"확장-프로그램-추천\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%99%95%EC%9E%A5-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%A8-%EC%B6%94%EC%B2%9C\" aria-label=\"확장 프로그램 추천 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>확장 프로그램 추천</h3>\n<p><strong>1. Collapsible headings:</strong> markdown header에 따라 노트북 접기 기능을 제공한다.</p>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 690px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/9f4842452c91c38868b1ebaa921e0186/01645/jupyter-notebook-install-1.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 50.28901734104046%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"jupyter notebook install 1\" title=\"jupyter notebook install 1\" src=\"/static/9f4842452c91c38868b1ebaa921e0186/1e043/jupyter-notebook-install-1.png\" srcset=\"/static/9f4842452c91c38868b1ebaa921e0186/991de/jupyter-notebook-install-1.png 173w,\n/static/9f4842452c91c38868b1ebaa921e0186/e4d6b/jupyter-notebook-install-1.png 345w,\n/static/9f4842452c91c38868b1ebaa921e0186/1e043/jupyter-notebook-install-1.png 690w,\n/static/9f4842452c91c38868b1ebaa921e0186/e3189/jupyter-notebook-install-1.png 1035w,\n/static/9f4842452c91c38868b1ebaa921e0186/01645/jupyter-notebook-install-1.png 1091w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<br/>\n<p><strong>2. Table of Conents:</strong> markdown header 수준에 따른 목차를 생성해준다.</p>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 690px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/9971d88f2dd0e0c6bf3d15d8190fd16c/2e367/jupyter-notebook-install-2.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.64739884393063%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"jupyter notebook install 2\" title=\"jupyter notebook install 2\" src=\"/static/9971d88f2dd0e0c6bf3d15d8190fd16c/1e043/jupyter-notebook-install-2.png\" srcset=\"/static/9971d88f2dd0e0c6bf3d15d8190fd16c/991de/jupyter-notebook-install-2.png 173w,\n/static/9971d88f2dd0e0c6bf3d15d8190fd16c/e4d6b/jupyter-notebook-install-2.png 345w,\n/static/9971d88f2dd0e0c6bf3d15d8190fd16c/1e043/jupyter-notebook-install-2.png 690w,\n/static/9971d88f2dd0e0c6bf3d15d8190fd16c/e3189/jupyter-notebook-install-2.png 1035w,\n/static/9971d88f2dd0e0c6bf3d15d8190fd16c/2e367/jupyter-notebook-install-2.png 1066w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<br/>\n<p><strong>3. code folding</strong></p>\n<p><strong>4. code prettify</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"4-virtual-environment-in-jupyter-notebook-kernel\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-virtual-environment-in-jupyter-notebook-kernel\" aria-label=\"4 virtual environment in jupyter notebook kernel permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. Virtual Environment in Jupyter notebook kernel</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">conda</code> 프롬프트에서 아래 명령어를 통해 가상환경을 만들 수 있다.</p>\n<h4 id=\"1-가상환경-추가--activate\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EA%B0%80%EC%83%81%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80--activate\" aria-label=\"1 가상환경 추가  activate permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 가상환경 추가 / activate</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">activate VENV_NAME</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"2-ipykernel-라이브러리-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-ipykernel-%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%8C%EB%9F%AC%EB%A6%AC-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"2 ipykernel 라이브러리 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 'ipykernel' 라이브러리 설치</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">pip <span class=\"token function\">install</span> ipykernel</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"3-커널-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EC%BB%A4%EB%84%90-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"3 커널 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.4